data.description: Nestled within the prestigious Gladden Farms community, this property epitomizes modern luxury and sustainable living. Situated on a premium lot, it ensures privacy with no rear neighbors, providing an atmosphere of tranquility. Step outside to your private oasis, complete with a refreshing pool, shaded ramada, and a lush, real grass lawn, creating a haven for relaxation and entertaining. Embrace a greener future with a leased Tesla solar system saving on energy bills. Inside, the vaulted ceilings and open floor plan create a spacious and inviting environment, and the modern kitchen, equipped with high-end appliances and a central island, makes daily living a pleasure. This Gladden Farms gem offers the ultimate in luxurious, sustainable living--don't miss your chance to call it home.
